FreeGeek is hosting a joint Holiday and Vintage Computing Party on Saturday, December 13th from
2p to 6p. We'll be ordering our standard fare of pizza and chicken to chomp on, though you're also
encouraged to bring a dish from home (especially Holiday treats and vegan dishes).
Much of FreeGeek's collection of vintage computers and game systems will be on display and available for sale. Jim Mazurek has
